dct_description_sm: U.S. Geological Survey map, Long Beach sheet in Ocean County, New Jersey. Surveyed in 1883, 1913 reprint of Aug. 1893 edition.
Fraying and tears along edges. File Copy written in pencil along with shelving notation.
